hr.fer.zemris.java.custom.scripting.nodes

Interface INodeVisitor


  • public interface INodeVisitor
    A visitor interface for Node extending classes' visitors.

    Supports visiting all known Node children. Implementing classes should take care of tree traversal as accept() function in Node classes don't have implemented the traversal.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Juraj Pejnovic
    See Also:
    Node
